      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلْمُسْلِمِ هَلْ يَرِثُ اَلْمُشْرِكَ فَقَالَ \"نَعَمْ فَأَمَّا اَلْمُشْرِكُ فَلاَ يَرِثُ اَلْمُسْلِمَ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5722 - Zurah narrated from Samaah from Abu Abdullah (as) who said:\nI asked Imam (as) whether a Muslim can inherit from a polytheist.\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes, but a polytheist does not inherit from a Muslim.\""
        ]
      }
